## Sanitise line endings for contributors using different OS ##

# Set the default behaviour, in case people don't have core.autocrlf set.
* text=auto

# Declare files that will always have *nix line endings on checkout.
*.csv text eol=lf

# Denote all files that are truly binary and should not be modified.
# (binary is a macro for -text -diff)
*.hex binary
*.png binary
*.ttf binary
*.zip binary